    "location": "Situated on the charming and picturesque Pago de la Paja road, between Route 104 and Eguzquiza Road, this property offers unparalleled access to the region's most attractive destinations: just 10 minutes from La Barra and Manantiales, 20 minutes from José Ignacio, 30 minutes from Punta del Este, and only 5 minutes from San Carlos.",
    "details": "The 400 m² main residence showcases excellent construction and thoughtful design focused on comfort and functionality. It features two spacious master suites with walk-in closets, a fully equipped gourmet kitchen, expansive living room, dining room, powder room, and service quarters. The social area is complemented by a barbecue area, laundry room, and a swimming pool, offering ideal spaces to enjoy the natural surroundings."
